A very simplified version of the CyclicRainbow results from Petzoldt's Ph.D.
thesis, written as an assignment for a research methodology class.

Disclaimer: this is *not* meant to replace nor plagiarize the original works.
It is simply a way to train academic-style writing and exercise the
understanding of the underlying subject. Refer to the bibliography file for
pointers to the thesis and papers.

